OL,3,CWorkers at Tetley Tea factory walk out
OL,4,Cover pay
OL,6,FWorkers at a Tetley Tea factory on
OL,7,FTeesside have walked out on strike.
OL,9,FThe industrial action by around 150
OL,10,Fmembers of the GMB Union based at the
OL,11,FEaglescliffe site is in a dispute over
OL,12,Fwhat the union has called "poverty
OL,13,Fpay."
OL,15,FTata Consumer Products, which makes
OL,16,FTetley said it believes that the pay
OL,17,Foffers made to workers are fair and
OL,18,Fare urging unions to reconsider their
OL,19,Fposition.
