OL,3,CWorkers at Tetley Tea factory walk out
OL,4,Cover pay
OL,6,FWorkers previously walked out last
OL,7,Fmonth and have announced another
OL,8,Fsingle day strike next week.
OL,10,FPaul Clark, a GMB Organiser, said:
OL,11,F"These women work their fingers to the
OL,12,Fbone for this company, providing the
OL,13,FUK with its favourite cup of tea.
OL,15,F"But they're paid a pittance and it is
OL,16,Fjust not right.
