OL,3,CWorkers at Tetley Tea factory walk out
OL,4,Cover pay
OL,6,F"Tata bosses need to be clear; these
OL,7,Fwomen will not be intimidated and will
OL,8,Fnot back down until they've won a pay
OL,9,Frise that allows them a decent
OL,10,Fstandard of living."
OL,12,FIn response a spokesperson for Tata
OL,13,FConsumer Products said: "We are not
OL,14,Fimmune to the difficult economic
OL,15,Fcircumstances facing families and
OL,16,Fbusinesses, but we do believe the pay
OL,17,Faward offers made by us to be fair.
