OL,6,F"We are urging the unions to
OL,7,Freconsider their position and present
OL,8,Fthe two offers on the table for
OL,9,Fconsideration by members so that we
OL,10,Fcan reach a swift resolution in line
OL,11,Fwith what's reasonably affordable to
OL,12,Fthe business, and in the best
OL,13,Finterests of the factory.
OL,15,FIt added: "We are committed to our UK
OL,16,Fmanufacturing base and are continuing
OL,17,Fto invest to expand its capabilities
OL,18,Fand further our sustainability agenda.
